                    <span>I recommend you to read other books before this one. This should be your second book. It explains some of AppWizard's code (Good Thing) but not too much as I expected. If your starting I recommend you to buy another book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Not so good as the average rate says.</div>
